      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WSRC    7
      *
S0   C           WO7       IFEQ *BLANK
      *
     C                     MOVEL'N'       WKUBN   1
     C                     SETOF                     88
     C           WO4       LOKUPTB1                      88
     C   88                MOVEL'O'       WKUBN   1
